{
    "poem_title": "Le Cimetière marin",
    "author": "Paul Valéry",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1922",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Ce toit tranquille, où marchent des colombes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Entre les pins palpite, entre les tombes ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Midi le juste y compose de feux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "La mer, la mer, toujours recommencée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Ô récompense après une pensée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Qu’un long regard sur le calme des dieux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ce toit tranquille, où marchent des colombes,\nEntre les pins palpite, entre les tombes ;\nMidi le juste y compose de feux\nLa mer, la mer, toujours recommencée\nÔ récompense après une pensée\nQu’un long regard sur le calme des dieux !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Quel pur travail de fins éclairs consume",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Maint diamant d’imperceptible écume,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Et quelle paix semble se concevoir !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Quand sur l’abîme un soleil se repose,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Ouvrages purs d’une éternelle cause,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Le Temps scintille et le Songe est savoir.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quel pur travail de fins éclairs consume\nMaint diamant d’imperceptible écume,\nEt quelle paix semble se concevoir !\nQuand sur l’abîme un soleil se repose,\nOuvrages purs d’une éternelle cause,\nLe Temps scintille et le Songe est savoir."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Stable trésor, temple simple à Minerve,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Masse de calme, et visible réserve,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Eau sourcilleuse, Œil qui gardes en toi",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Tant de sommeil sous un voile de flamme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Ô mon silence !… Édifice dans l’âme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Mais comble d’or aux mille tuiles, Toit !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Stable trésor, temple simple à Minerve,\nMasse de calme, et visible réserve,\nEau sourcilleuse, Œil qui gardes en toi\nTant de sommeil sous un voile de flamme,\nÔ mon silence !… Édifice dans l’âme,\nMais comble d’or aux mille tuiles, Toit !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Temple du Temps, qu’un seul soupir résume,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "À ce point pur je monte et m’accoutume,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Tout entouré de mon regard marin ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Et comme aux dieux mon offrande suprême,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "La scintillation sereine sème",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+4",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Sur l’altitude un dédain souverain.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Temple du Temps, qu’un seul soupir résume,\nÀ ce point pur je monte et m’accoutume,\nTout entouré de mon regard marin ;\nEt comme aux dieux mon offrande suprême,\nLa scintillation sereine sème\nSur l’altitude un dédain souverain."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Comme le fruit se fond en jouissance,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Comme en délice il change son absence",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Dans une bouche où sa forme se meurt,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Je hume ici ma future fumée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Et le ciel chante à l’âme consumée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Le changement des rives en rumeur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Comme le fruit se fond en jouissance,\nComme en délice il change son absence\nDans une bouche où sa forme se meurt,\nJe hume ici ma future fumée,\nEt le ciel chante à l’âme consumée\nLe changement des rives en rumeur."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Beau ciel, vrai ciel, regarde-moi qui change !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Après tant d’orgueil, après tant d’étrange",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "10",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Oisiveté, mais pleine de pouvoir,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Je m’abandonne à ce brillant espace,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Sur les maisons des morts mon ombre passe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Qui m’apprivoise à son frêle mouvoir.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Beau ciel, vrai ciel, regarde-moi qui change !\nAprès tant d’orgueil, après tant d’étrange\nOisiveté, mais pleine de pouvoir,\nJe m’abandonne à ce brillant espace,\nSur les maisons des morts mon ombre passe\nQui m’apprivoise à son frêle mouvoir."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "L’âme exposée aux torches du solstice,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Je te soutiens, admirable justice",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "De la lumière aux armes sans pitié !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Je te tends pure à ta place première,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Regarde-toi !… Mais rendre la lumière",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Suppose d’ombre une morne moitié.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "L’âme exposée aux torches du solstice,\nJe te soutiens, admirable justice\nDe la lumière aux armes sans pitié !\nJe te tends pure à ta place première,\nRegarde-toi !… Mais rendre la lumière\nSuppose d’ombre une morne moitié."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Ô pour moi seul, à moi seul, en moi-même,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Auprès d’un cœur, aux sources du poème,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Entre le vide et l’événement pur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "J’attends l’écho de ma grandeur interne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Amère, sombre, et sonore citerne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Sonnant dans l’âme un creux toujours futur !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ô pour moi seul, à moi seul, en moi-même,\nAuprès d’un cœur, aux sources du poème,\nEntre le vide et l’événement pur,\nJ’attends l’écho de ma grandeur interne,\nAmère, sombre, et sonore citerne,\nSonnant dans l’âme un creux toujours futur !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Sais-tu, fausse captive des feuillages,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+4",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Golfe mangeur de ces maigres grillages,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Sur mes yeux clos, secrets éblouissants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Quel corps me traîne à sa fin paresseuse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Quel front l’attire à cette terre osseuse ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Une étincelle y pense à mes absents.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sais-tu, fausse captive des feuillages,\nGolfe mangeur de ces maigres grillages,\nSur mes yeux clos, secrets éblouissants,\nQuel corps me traîne à sa fin paresseuse,\nQuel front l’attire à cette terre osseuse ?\nUne étincelle y pense à mes absents."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Fermé, sacré, plein d’un feu sans matière,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Fragment terrestre offert à la lumière,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Ce lieu me plaît, dominé de flambeaux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Composé d’or, de pierre et d’arbres sombres,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Où tant de marbre est tremblant sur tant d’ombres ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "La mer fidèle y dort sur mes tombeaux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Fermé, sacré, plein d’un feu sans matière,\nFragment terrestre offert à la lumière,\nCe lieu me plaît, dominé de flambeaux,\nComposé d’or, de pierre et d’arbres sombres,\nOù tant de marbre est tremblant sur tant d’ombres ;\nLa mer fidèle y dort sur mes tombeaux !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Chienne splendide, écarte l’idolâtre !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Quand solitaire au sourire de pâtre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Je pais longtemps, moutons mystérieux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Le blanc troupeau de mes tranquilles tombes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Éloignes-en les prudentes colombes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Les songes vains, les anges curieux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Chienne splendide, écarte l’idolâtre !\nQuand solitaire au sourire de pâtre,\nJe pais longtemps, moutons mystérieux,\nLe blanc troupeau de mes tranquilles tombes,\nÉloignes-en les prudentes colombes,\nLes songes vains, les anges curieux !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Ici venu, l’avenir est paresse.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "L’insecte net gratte la sécheresse ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Tout est brûlé, défait, reçu dans l’air",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "À je ne sais quelle sévère essence…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "La vie est vaste, étant ivre d’absence,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Et l’amertume est douce, et l’esprit clair.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ici venu, l’avenir est paresse.\nL’insecte net gratte la sécheresse ;\nTout est brûlé, défait, reçu dans l’air\nÀ je ne sais quelle sévère essence…\nLa vie est vaste, étant ivre d’absence,\nEt l’amertume est douce, et l’esprit clair."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "Les morts cachés sont bien dans cette terre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "Qui les réchauffe et sèche leur mystère.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "Midi là-haut, Midi sans mouvement",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "En soi se pense et convient à soi-même…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Tête complète et parfait diadème,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Je suis en toi le secret changement.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les morts cachés sont bien dans cette terre\nQui les réchauffe et sèche leur mystère.\nMidi là-haut, Midi sans mouvement\nEn soi se pense et convient à soi-même…\nTête complète et parfait diadème,\nJe suis en toi le secret changement."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 14,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Tu n’as que moi pour contenir tes craintes !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Mes repentirs, mes doutes, mes contraintes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "Sont le défaut de ton grand diamant…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 82,
                    "line_text": "Mais dans leur nuit toute lourde de marbres,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 83,
                    "line_text": "Un peuple vague aux racines des arbres",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 84,
                    "line_text": "A pris déjà ton parti lentement.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
